values:
I got into the way of felling emptiness that I didn't realised it for several month or years. Probably I've found it when my close friend said: "You are really cruel". I thought that she is joking or something. She was serious, but I can not be a such of kind as I help people and don't wait anything in feedback. So I asked her: "Is it good or bad?". She said:"I don't know, probably good". 
So why emptiness? Emptiness is like cruelty (they are sis). It's easy to come to that inside as you just try to dissolve in nothing. Just stop and all you faithfullness, emotional experience throw in nothing. If you practice, it's relly-really easy ). 
But then after long time you come to conclusion that you are not able to feel anything. 
It's good but just a little. I think I've lost myself somewhere.
I cann't love anyone except my parents. Not because of past experience but because I've used to it (that really easy). But the most important for me people (parents) will suffer because I knowingly lose connection (without any scandals).
